 А                                                                           А
 А  Vero Software, the worlds largest and number one CAM specialist is      А
 А  pleased to announce the acquisition of the SURFCAM assets from           А
 А  Surfware, Inc., a US based software specialist responsible for the       А
 А  development of SURFCAM and the award-winning TRUEMill technology.        А
 А                                                                           А
 А  Commenting on the acquisition, Richard Smith, CEO of Vero Software       А
 А  says, "Across the enlarged Group, the complementary products address     А
 А  the worldwide need for efficient and innovative CAD/CAM/CAE              А
 А  technology. SURFCAM is a robust, and well respected CAD/CAM system       А
 А  with a large number of loyal customers and knowledgeable resellers.      А
 А  With an emphasis on sharing already proven technologies, we will         А
 А  provide the development platform to reinvigorate the SURFCAM             А
 А  product and continue to help its customers become more efficient,        А
 А  profitable and successful. Following our recent European                 А
 А  acquisition of Sescoi (WorkNC), this US acquisition is further           А
 А  evidence of our growing influence on the global manufacturing            А
 А  market. We fully recognise the importance of product branding            А
 А  and it is important to emphasise that we will continue to invest         А
 А  in SURFCAM through our new subsidiary Surfcam Inc., and welcome          А
 А  the existing US and overseas Surfware partners and resellers             А
 А  into the Vero network."Alan Diehl and his son Larry originally           А
 А  founded Surfware in 1988, with Alans other son Bryan joining            А
 А  the company in 1990.  Regarding the change, Alan says, We have          А
 А  dedicated our lives to developing innovative and productive              А
 А  machining technology. Just as importantly, we enjoy customer and         А
 А  reseller relationships that are the envy of our competitors. We          А
 А  know we are joining a group with a similar view. We are confident        А
 А  that Veros additional resources and global distribution will take       А
 А  SURFCAM to new levels of efficiency, and will continue to provide        А
 А  solutions that boost our customers productivity, reduce costs           А
 А  and improve quality. "                                                   А
